    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We’ll soon see the Lord, as He is, face to face,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We’ll know Him as never before;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But that touch today, healing our broken heart,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In that day will be felt no more."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That day, though our lips offer unceasing praise,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "No tears, then, nor prayers fervent burn;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Nor is there the comfort received through much pain,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Nor trust gained through trials to learn,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Nor trust gained through trials to learn."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Exceeding in glory, that day we’ll be crowned,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Yet there’ll be no cross to obey;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The sweet fellowship of His suff’rings for us"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We only can share in today."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Once we’ve that rest entered, no weariness then,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Nor chance will remain to partake"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The trials nor the hardships, nor happiness lost,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Nor suffering borne for His sake,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Nor suffering borne for His sake."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Oh, chances to suffer for Him are so few,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "His shame and derision to bear;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Such blest opportunities soon pass away,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That He in our troubles may share."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All loneliness, misunderstandings and scorn"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Despisings and sorrows will flee;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I treasure these blessings, for through them, O Lord,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I enter sweet oneness with Thee,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I enter sweet oneness with Thee."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I long to behold, Lord, Thy countenance soon,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "What rapture with Thee, Lord, to meet."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But neither seek I all these trials to avoid;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Such times, Lord, are too rare and sweet."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Have mercy on me, fill me with Thy great love,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For Thee, Lord, to live at all cost;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lest Thy servant, hoping for that blessed day,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That day, regret chances were lost,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That day, regret chances were lost."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
